import Head from 'next/head'
import styles from './index.module.css'
import { Container, Row, Col, Navbar, Nav, NavDropdown, Form, FormControl, Button } from 'react-bootstrap'

const Home = () => (
  <>
    <Container className="container-fluid">
      <Row className="w-100">
        <Col className={`col-xl-8 h-100 d-inline-block ${styles.maincontent}`}>
          Main Content
        </Col>
        <Col className={`col-xl-4 h-100 d-inline-block ${styles.sidebar}`}>
          Sidebar
        </Col>
      </Row>
    </Container>

  </>
)

export default Home
